    {
      "code": "P98",
      "type": "DesignNote",
      "value": "Glioblastoma is not an astrocytoma. It is an astrocytic tumor. The latter includes astrocytomas and glioblastomas.  However, when an anaplastic astrocytoma progresses to grade IV tumor, it is called a glioblastoma."
